# ASPIS two-git separation (F-022 / D-023): the AI workspace and the runtime dirs
# are versioned outside this product repo. The brain keeps its own git history in
# .aspis/.git (the shadow repo); the runtime dirs are catalog-rendered and tracked by
# content hashes + a change-log. None of it belongs in the product's public history.
.aspis/
.opencode/
.claude/

# >>> aspis gitignore (python) >>>
